data.description: This charming renovated 3BR/2BA ranch home incorporates a spacious renovated dining room that opens to the kitchen. The renovated kitchen features gorgeous granite countertops, tall white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Beautiful hardwood flooring flows throughout the renovated family room and throughout the home. Three expansive bedrooms with hardwood flooring and two renovated bathrooms both featuring decorative tiles and fine details. The entire interior of the home has been renovated and awaits a new homeowner. This 4 sided brick home has a new roof and is encompassed by a large wooded backyard which is a canvas for any outdoor idea that you may have and a large front yard with.
